Package: cdiscmask
Title: Anonymize CDISC Clinical Trial Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Anonymizes CDISC-standard datasets (SDTM, ADaM) while preserving
    data types and cross-domain consistency. Subject identifiers are replaced
    with pseudonyms, dates are shifted by a per-subject random offset applied
    uniformly across all domains, and a reversible key is stored so that
    original data can be recovered. Sensitive columns are detected automatically
    based on CDISC variable naming conventions.
